      "body" : "People also regularly confuse options that affect the wallet with those that affect block chain indexing.\r\nWhich is not strange; `-rescan` and -`reindex` both sound the same, from the name you wouldn't guess they do entirely different things. 'namespacing' the options by what they affect would have been a good idea.\r\nThen again, at least that problem will go away when the wallet is separate.\r\n\r\n",
